ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
SubjectVolatile Organic Compound (VOC) Concentration Limits for Automotive Refinishing Products Regulations
PrecisVOLATILE ORGANIC COMPOUND (VOC) CONCENTRATION LIMITS FOR AUTOMOTIVE REFINISHING PRODUCTS REGULATIONS to protect the environment and health of Canadians from the effects of air pollution by establishing VOC concentration limits for 14 categories of automotive refinishing products for use in Canada.
